{"tid":458558,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"傳大陸回收價已跌穿原價","createTime":"2017-11-05T04:00:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-05T05:20:26.000Z","uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"937ca4114f9d43cb74a74c9236b74641ad6eccf4","tid":458558,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T04:00:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/article/130961/thumbnail/e42aa7f2be98fcb107fc07dca26ddb8c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Farticle%2F130961%2Fthumbnail%2Fe42aa7f2be98fcb107fc07dca26ddb8c.jpg&h=e07a5ca8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n每逢推出新款iPhone，總有一眾「果農」狂搶希望大撈一筆，今年備受矚目的iPhone X在預售日極速售罄，但回收價格不如預期。今天先達廣場「收市」，所有iPhone X機款回收價已急跌至接近原價，出售256GB機款尚可賺100多元，64GB機款最慘只有10多元「水位」，甚至有少部分店舖停收iPhone X。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/955430/xlarge/7240da0eaca21753bd71cc9d1005a4ab.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F955430%2Fxlarge%2F7240da0eaca21753bd71cc9d1005a4ab.jpg&h=0d87f346&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n旺角先達廣場於iPhone X發售翌日，依然人頭湧湧。（廖迪莎攝）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/953912/xlarge/b0d897f076fc2fdc851d5dcd00deca9c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F953912%2Fxlarge%2Fb0d897f076fc2fdc851d5dcd00deca9c.jpg&h=e9f0d179&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/951685/xlarge/c7a89debe084864f5f55ab78a667ea33.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F951685%2Fxlarge%2Fc7a89debe084864f5f55ab78a667ea33.jpg&h=ebb2948f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/951590/xlarge/8a58520335997d8966468e591c70bd3e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F951590%2Fxlarge%2F8a58520335997d8966468e591c70bd3e.jpg&h=d08619c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/953445/xlarge/56ccf938abd6eb061456dd2e1e786a63.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F953445%2Fxlarge%2F56ccf938abd6eb061456dd2e1e786a63.jpg&h=c3729131&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/952148/xlarge/a60e0942be630212cb2384f4a5611c34.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F952148%2Fxlarge%2Fa60e0942be630212cb2384f4a5611c34.jpg&h=0287cf54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今日（4日）的旺角先達廣場到黃昏依然人頭湧湧，不過兩種機款的回收價都已跌至接近原價，綜合各店價錢，256GB（原價9,888元）及64GB（原價8,588元）機款的回收價，分別維持於10000元至10200元，以及8600元至8700元。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/955438/xlarge/747c5bd08e41b9f4b46f97ab8a037d69.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F955438%2Fxlarge%2F747c5bd08e41b9f4b46f97ab8a037d69.jpg&h=f463d1d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n先達收市時，iPhone X回收價跌近原價。（廖迪莎攝）<br />\n<br />\n炒價慘淡，甚至有少部分店舖停收iPhone X。萬通數碼電訊東主阿K指，今天已有150人至200人到「放機」，不過他明言現時回收的手機數已滿足訂單，除非再有新訂單，否則不會冒險收機。<br />\n<br />\n今年新款iPhone回收行情比以往慘淡，阿K認為源於大陸貨源太足，又指現時大陸iPhone X的回收價甚至已低於原價。他亦不看好iPhone未來的行情，直言中港同步發售的新政策是錯誤的決定，因為這令手機失去神秘感，炒風不再，影響整個亞洲地區銷情。<br />\n<br />\n雖然先達廣場的回收價已跌近原價，現場仍有不少市民尋覓回收店舖，擔心電話無法售出，但亦有不少人因回收價太低而十分猶豫。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/955443/xlarge/2c7da4406fd1b04525f220b4e409548d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F955443%2Fxlarge%2F2c7da4406fd1b04525f220b4e409548d.jpg&h=fbc33459&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n現場仍有不少市民尋覓回收店舖，擔心電話無法售出，顯得心急。（廖迪莎攝）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/130961/iPhone-X%E7%82%92%E5%83%B9%E6%A5%B5%E6%85%98-%E5%81%9C%E6%94%B6%E6%96%B0%E6%A9%9F%E5%85%88%E9%81%94%E6%89%8B%E6%A9%9F%E5%BA%97-%E5%82%B3%E5%A4%A7%E9%99%B8%E5%9B%9E%E6%94%B6%E5%83%B9%E5%B7%B2%E8%B7%8C%E7%A9%BF%E5%8E%9F%E5%83%B9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%2